Author: dragaynite
Text: Wow your friend is seriously manipulative and ignorant. To threaten something as serious as wanting to kill her self over your mental struggles is just appalling. I’m sorry you’re in this situation, I hope everything gets better and you can get the help you need/want :/

Author: DesperateLyingFox
Text: Nothing I will say will help you right now. But, I totally understand your feelings, the anger, feeling helpless, wanting to be sicker than ever.  But I hope you will reflect this situation and get the help you need. You are sick enough to need help. Stay safe and good luck ☹️
